{"tid":1559302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【置頂正視聽】整場運動無走向衰亡，而係走向成功而我地不知所措","createTime":"2019-09-10T18:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T18:22:06.000Z","uid":218570,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25c58b07dbfc74ba177a8f6304bca390a797cd32","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:08:03.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">原文來自 山本小鐵子 巴打\n想大家幫手置頂 每日為香港人打氣！</code></pre><br />\n我地必須要接受一個事實，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何事都有完結既一日</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地總有一日都會放低豬咀，放低黑衫，放低勇武<br />\n重新過番正常生活番工番學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問題係件事點完結，係我地全軍覆沒，定係革命成功<br />\n我可以好肯定話你知，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地正正係成功方向，天時地利係晒我地到</span></span><br />\n問題係，由佔中，魚革開始，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地係從來未成功過</span><br />\n我地成日打逆境波，但對於係上風既時候點做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地係完全無經驗</span><br />\n所以我地完全係唔知點做，無焦點，好多人會出黎騎劫<br />\n但唔緊要，只要穩打穩扎，我地一樣會成功，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最緊要係個心態，唔好ＤＯＷＮ唔好放棄</span><br />\n我地正正係進入緊一個完全未知既時代<br />\n呢個轉變，六十後未見過，七十後未見過，八十後未見過，九十後未見過，零零後都未見過<br />\n命運真係好公平，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時代革命面前，人人平等</span></span>，大家都係ＢＢ仔<br />\n當大家都唔知點知，就BACK TO BASIC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重建文宣</span></span><br />\n而家大部分連農牆無人貼野無人理<br />\n我地要整D<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更加JUICY,更加長輩圖,更加血腥既文宣</span></span><br />\n今日鍾國斌同支那官割席既,就大大張POSTER大大隻字寫比警犬,廢老同藍絲睇<br />\n要佢地士氣低落,警犬,廢老同藍絲係勝利球迷,只會比人愈打愈DUP<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">慢慢佢地自己都會懷疑自己不攻自破</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有十點鐘,有野做無野做好都同我大大聲嗌時代革命同唱國歌,我地自己既士氣係好重要</span></span><br />\n而且唔好再出D咩失敗呀,敗亡呀,衰亡呀<br />\n民氣一走個運動就真係收皮<br />\n有咩野唔順意,記撚住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港,時代革命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文link:<br />\n【正視聽】整場運動無走向衰亡，而係走向成功而我地不知所措<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇過嘅麻煩幫手推推post<br />\n幫未睇過嘅巴打加加油"},{"pid":"ab3e5bba7e1d69ad97b77e7fcf160a9cee488863","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:08:16.000Z","msg":"1/50"},{"pid":"1646bcc4852241d90d50d192ce41d398d289a7c9","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"2/50"},{"pid":"a136809995c6de741db078c8456a3e6589ff5438","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:08:37.000Z","msg":"3/50"},{"pid":"3c3a72756dd3a5bfc9cc61802b66d5ba52fa9553","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:08:48.000Z","msg":"4/50"},{"pid":"e9d2420fa436581f92ed2d7fa00cbd2290c947a4","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:09:00.000Z","msg":"5/50"},{"pid":"05114746c44f9be12465e9131d130cd9f059ae73","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:09:21.000Z","msg":"6/50"},{"pid":"bdf3aed6ce634f5f64e3dab56472930141a3e7c2","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:09:34.000Z","msg":"7/50"},{"pid":"0f6cc8421988b2d9b42792550396c6e4b355b6b7","tid":1559302,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"